00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:09.290
The regulation EU number 1257 Stroke 2013 of
the European Parliament on ship recycling was

2
00:00:09.290 --> 00:00:14.540
published in the official Journal of the
European Union on the 10th of December 2013.

3
00:00:14.570 --> 00:00:21.320
This regulation is also called EU Ship
Recycling Regulation or EU SR.

4
00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:28.160
The EU ship recycling Regulation entered
into force at the end of 2013 with a phase in

5
00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:35.150
period between the 31st of December 2015 and
the 31st of December 2020.